00:53:11,855 --> 00:53:14,153
Okay. - Okay wish you all
the best. - Thanks.

537
00:53:16,693 --> 00:53:20,151
She won't listen. I had told you
not to play in the rain.

538
00:53:20,363 --> 00:53:22,490
Suppose you catch old,
have fever...

