570
01:01:20,677 --> 01:01:35,149
I'll not leave you. You've killed
my Munna, I'll kill you...

571
01:01:35,358 --> 01:01:39,317
You've broken the dam you've
killed by Munna.

572
01:01:40,029 --> 01:01:44,557
I'll not leave you.
You've killed my Munna...

